---
// Used to list all unique tags
// goal to have little counter next to each one showing how
// many times the tag has been used
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
const posts = await getCollection('blog');

import Tags from "./Tags.astro";

// getting unique tags
const uniqueTags = [
  ...new Set(posts.map((post) => post.tags).flat()),
];
const seo = {
  title: "Tags",
  description: "A list of all tags used sitewide for blog posts and images",
};
---

<Tags tags={uniqueTags} />
